Hmm... in a different section of the ebook it says; 

The Communicate Fix UI action may be used to copy the text from the Fix notes field of the problem record to associated incidents. By default, the fix notes get copied to incidents that are New, On Hold, or In Progress. 

And in the image, it shows the comment going in Work Notes. So, It looks like A is the closets though it's work notes. Given all work notes are comments but not all comments are work notes, I guess the answer is A.
